	<li>Cryptography and PKI</li>
	<li>Wireless security</li>
	<li>Intrusion detection/prevention</li>
</ul>
<h3>Topic Area: Security Management</h3>
<p>Organizing and managing the information security function is relatively new to higher education IT departments. It can be a challenge in an academic environment in terms of finding both staff and funding. In addition, it is useful to learn how others have garnered support and buy-in and have obtained guidance for the information assurance mission. </p>
<p>Key topics include:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Information security office staffing and organization</li>
