<h3>Topic Area: Regulatory Compliance</h3>
<p>Emerging legal, ethical, and appropriate information use issues have placed a higher priority on the development of policies and other response strategies at our institutions, including the need to respond to legislation and regulation. It is useful to learn how others have garnered support and buy-in in efforts to ensure regulatory compliance. </p>
